Watching this video left  you a feeling of Pure  amazement and  AH ! ! It  is truly amazing that a Series of Construction Projects of this magnitude could be Simultaneously conducted and completed within a very short period of eight years !!! If this Project we're going to be done in the USA
It would take 25 years with all of the BS and Political Red tape of State and local Governments and The Wining Environmentalists who would like nothing more to see a Construction Projet of this Size stoped beforever the Project ever got started ... Steve jones
This video is quite informative , providing insights into the development of the Chep Lap Kok Airport in Hong Kong.
